">switch</span><span class="s8"> </span>switchValue<span class="s8"> {</span></p><p class="p2">&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="s2">case</span> <span class="s5">&quot;a&quot;</span>:</p><p class="p2">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="s7">println</span>(<span class="s5">&quot;a&quot;</span>)</p><p class="p2">&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="s2">case</span> <span class="s5">&quot;b&quot;</span>:</p><p class="p2">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="s7">println</span>(<span class="s5">&quot;b&quot;</span>)</p><p class="p6"><span class="s8">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span>default<span class="s8">:</span></p><p class="p2">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="s7">println</span>(<span class="s5">&quot;d&quot;</span>)</p><p class="p2">}</p><p class="p3"><span class="s4">//</span>判断多个值不能写：</p><p class="p1">//case &quot;a&quot;:</p><p class="p1">//case &quot;A&quot;:</p><p class="p1">//&nbsp; println(&quot;ok&quot;);</p><p class="p3"><span class="s4">//</span>而是应该写：</p><p class="p1">//case &quot;a&quot;, &quot;A&quot;:</p><p class="p2" style="white-space: normal;">[/code]</p><p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;">&nbsp; &nbsp; switch高级特性相关的如下：</p><p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;">[code]</p><p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;">/**</p><p class="p1">&nbsp;* switch<span class="s1">高级特性</span></p><p class="p1">&nbsp;*/</p><p class="p1">//<span class="s1">元组在</span>switch<span class="s1">中</span></p><p class="p3"><span class="s4">//</span>如果想执行第一个<span class="s4">case</span>后还想执行第二个<span class="s4">case</span>，则添加<span class="s4">fallthrough</span>，此时直接进入下面的语句，不进行<span class="s4">case</span>判断</p><p class="p2"><span class="s2">var</span> request = (<span class="s2">true</span>, <span class="s5">&quot;success&quot;</span>)</p><p class="p7"><span class="s2">switch</span><span class="s8"> </span>request<span class="s8">{</span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s8">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span>//<span class="s1">这个是正确的</span></p><p class="p2">&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="s2">case</span> (<span class="s2">true</span>, <span class="s5">&quot;success&quot;</span>):</p><p class="p4"><span class="s8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span class="s7">println</span><span class="s8">(</span>&quot;true, success&quot;<span class="s8">)</span></p><p class="p6"><span class="s8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span>fallthrough</p><p class="p3"><span class="s9">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span class="s4">//</span>这个也是正确的，可以忽略元组的第一个元素，将剩下的元素判断</p><p class="p2">&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="s2">case</span> (<span class="s2">true</span>, <span class="s2">_</span>):</p><p class="p4"><span class="s8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span class="s7">println</span><span class="s8">(</span>&quot;true, success&quot;<span class="s8">)</span></p><p class="p3"><span class="s9">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span class="s4">//</span>这个也是正确的</p><p class="p2">&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="s2">case</span> (<span class="s2">true</span>, <span class="s2">let</span> requestStatus):</p><p class="p2">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="s7">println</span>(<span class="s5">&quot;</span><span class="s10">当前登陆状态为：</span>\\(requestStatus)<span class="s5">&quot;</span>);</p><p class="p6"><span class="s8">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span>default<span class="s8">:</span></p><p class="p4"><span class="s8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span class="s7">println</span><span class="s8">(</span>&quot;not found!&quot;<span class="s8">)</span></p><p class="p2">}</p><p class="p1">//switch<span class="s1">可以比较范围</span></p><p class="p2"><span class="s2">var</span> request2 = (<span class="s3">5</span>, <span class="s3">12</span>);</p><p class="p7"><span class="s2">switch</span><span class="s8"> </span>request2<span class="s8">{</span></p><p class="p2">&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="s2">case</span> (<span class="s3">1</span>...<span class="s3">8</span>, <span class="s3">10</span>...<span class="s3">20</span>):</p><p class="p2">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="s7">println</span>(<span class="s5">&quot;ok&quot;</span>)<